---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Whisk Bake Repeat">
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-amber-50 px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-rose-700">
        About
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-950 md:text-6xl">
        The story behind Whisk Bake Repeat
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-stone-700 md:text-lg">
        <p>
          This is where her longer about-me story can go. She can talk about how
          she started baking, what she loves making, and what makes each order
          personal.
        </p>

        <p>
          She can also include her baking style, favorite types of cakes, family
          inspiration, or what customers can expect when reaching out.
        </p>

        <p>
          Replace this with her real wording once she writes it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <a
          href="/#contact"
          class="rounded-full bg-rose-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-rose-800"
        >
          Ask About Availability
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>